  "description": "<p>Job Title: Waitress Supervisor (5-Star Hotel) (ID4759)<br />Location: City Hall<br />Working Hours: 5 days per week, 9.5 hours per day.(morning, afternoon, night shifts)<br />Salary : $3300-$3500<br /><br />Waitress Supervisor (5-Star Hotel)<br />Key Responsibilities :<br />• Supervised and coordinated daily service operations of waitstaff<br />• Assigned duties, scheduled shifts, and ensured adequate staffing<br />• Trained new staff on service standards, hygiene, and SOPs<br />• Ensured high standards of customer service and handled guest complaints<br />• Monitored food quality, service speed, and cleanliness of dining areas<br />• Assisted with cashiering, POS operations, and end-of-shift reports<br />• Worked closely with kitchen and management to ensure smooth operations<br />• Ensured compliance with health, safety, and company policies<br /><br />Requirements :<br />• Must have 1-3 years Waitress Supervisor experience<br />• Good customer service and communication skills</p>",
